From: Zumeng Chen <zumeng.chen@windriver.com>
Date: Fri, 14 Mar 2014 10:01:15 +0800
Subject: [PATCH 188/188] usb: musb: am335x need a connection right now

This patch is a workaround to start a session when role mode.

Signed-off-by: Zumeng Chen <zumeng.chen@windriver.com>
---
 drivers/usb/musb/musb_virthub.c |    5 +++++
 1 files changed, 5 insertions(+), 0 deletions(-)

diff --git a/drivers/usb/musb/musb_virthub.c b/drivers/usb/musb/musb_virthub.c
index ad417fd..a15312e 100644
--- a/drivers/usb/musb/musb_virthub.c
+++ b/drivers/usb/musb/musb_virthub.c
@@ -251,6 +251,7 @@ int musb_hub_status_data(struct usb_hcd *hcd, char *buf)
 	return retval;
 }
 
+extern int omap_type(void);
 static int musb_has_gadget(struct musb *musb)
 {
 	/*
@@ -259,6 +260,10 @@ static int musb_has_gadget(struct musb *musb)
 	 * gadget if we operate as a host but we should not start a session
 	 * as a device without a gadget or else we explode.
 	 */
+
+	if (omap_type() == 0x03)
+		return 1;
+
 #ifdef CONFIG_USB_MUSB_HOST
 	return 1;
 #else
